               <person xml:id="Elizabeth_Holland_Stevenson">
                  <persName>
                     <surname type="maiden">Holland</surname><surname/>
                     <surname type="married">Gaskell</surname>
                     <forename>Elizabeth</forename>
                  </persName>
                  <birth>
                     <placeName/>
                  </birth>
                  <death>
                     <date when="1811"></date>
                     <placeName/>
                  </death>
                  <note type="bio" resp="#mjk">
                     <p>Gaskell’s mother, fourth daughter and sixth child of Samuel and Anne Holland of Sandlebridge, in Knutsford. Tradition, passed down through narratives of family and friends, holds that only her first (John) and last (Elizabeth) of 8 children survived, though only John’s birth is registered. She died when Gaskell was 13 months old.</p>
                  </note></person>
               <person xml:id="John_Stevenson">
