                  <forename>John</forename>
                  </persName>
                  <birth when="1798-11-17">November 17 1798</birth>              
               <note resp="mjk"><p>Gaskell’s older brother; a sailor, was lost at sea or in India sometime in fall 1828.</p></note> </person>
               <person xml:id="Catherine_Thompson_Stevenson">
