                     <forename>Catherine</forename>
                  </persName>
                  <birth></birth>
                  <death></death>
                  <note><p>Gaskell’s stepmother. Gaskell saw little of her father after the marriage. Catherine’s  brother married Katherine Byerly, who founded the school Gaskell attended.</p></note>
